review_blob: Bit sweet on the nose, very sugary. Taste very sweet, syrupy. Hvfhjjng bgfdghhhh bhfhjghhvvvdsaw
Nice hopp aroma, not over the top, with hint of coffee and roast, only subtle though. Taste similar, nothing harsh or in your face. Just subtle. Nice beer.
beer_name: Clown Shoes Hoppy Feet Black IPA

review_blob: Big bitter coffee notes on the nose and tongue. Dark chock and roasty notes. Maybe a bit over done on these flavours, but perhaps thats why I liked it.

golden, medium sweetness, lightly bitter, light body, went into this rating with extremely low expectation, with previous memories of this beer being bad! And whereas it was far from good, it was not bad, basically just an easy drinking lolly water, was surprising to me. No way i would start drinking it though!
